<body>

  <!-- Header and Nav -->

<%= render :partial => 'layouts/nav' %>

  <!-- End Header and Nav -->


  <!-- First Band (Slider) -->
  <!-- The Orbit slider is initialized at the bottom of the page by calling .orbit() on #slider -->

  <div class="row">
    <div class="twelve columns">
      <div id="slider">
        <img src="/assets/tunrbanner1.jpg" />
        <img src="/assets/musicmontage1.jpg" />
      </div>

      <hr />
    </div>
  </div>


  <!-- Three-up Content Blocks -->

  <div class="row">

    <div class="four columns">
      <img src="/assets/tunr_square1.jpg" />
      <h4>About Tunr</h4>

      <%= yield %>

      <p>Tunr is your very own online music device for purchasing songs and creating playlists. The difference between Tunr and other music apps is that Tunr will actually refund you most of the purchase price of any song you have purchased. So if you no longer want a song in any of your playlists, simply got to the refunds page and your account will be credited with 70% of the original song cost.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="four columns">
      <img src="/assets/tunr_square2.jpg" />
      <h4>Featured playlists</h4>
      <p>Some of our users have been sharing their favorite playlists via our popular Tunr blog. Are you looking for some new music inspiration? Well check out the Tunr blog for the latest and most highly rated user playlists. You can search by genre, artist or album to find new songs that you want ot add to your collection.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="four columns">
      <img src="/assets/tunr_square3.jpg" />
      <h4>The week at Tunr</h4>
        <p>Every week here at Tunr we are dedicated to discovering the best new music out there. We've got all your old favorites and current hits, but what makes us different is that we'll bring to you music that is yet to be discovered. That's why we can offer such competitive prices and refund options.</p>
    </div>

  </div>


  <!-- Call to Action Panel -->
  <div class="row">
    <div class="twelve columns">

      <div class="panel">
        <h4>Get in touch!</h4>

        <div class="row">
          <div class="nine columns">
            <p>We'd love to hear from you, send us your feedback and we'll be sure to respond in song.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="three columns">
            <a href="#" class="radius button right">Contact Us</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>


  <!-- Footer -->

<%= render :partial => 'layouts/footer' %>

